name: #002 Nigel Mansell Williams 1992
description:
Nigel Mansell (1953-) is a British F1 driver.

He had 31 wins, 59 podiums, was pole position 32 times, and won 1 championship (1992). 

Driving Williams car FW14B, he was 2nd on the 92' Grand Prix! 

And Williams won the F1 Constructers World Championship!

When Mansell started racing, he won 5 races in a row!
